text.tspan: Schema for coloring the Pallet borders
start out making every pallet red?
my_var_0 = The pallets put into an array with ascending order of weight value
my_var_1 = Total pallet weight is divided by number of pallets to get the mean average of pallet weight (166)
my_var_2 = the pallet that occurs in ascending weight order right before my_var_1
my_var_3 = total number of pallets divided by three, rounded to the closest whole number,(4),
my_var_4 = my_var_3 divided by 2 once again, and rounded to the closest whole number(2)
my_var_9 = the lightest pallet is always green regardless of previous calculations
my_var_10 = the heaviest pallet is always red regardless of previous calculations
